data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION is key with this two-story colonial on the South end of Hanover.  New Roof. Southwestern schools. Close to conveniences and great for commuters. Quiet neighborhood with a spacious yard offering privacy and a beautiful paver patio you're going to love! This home features 4 beds, 2.5 baths and all the rooms you need for your family or for entertaining. 1st floor laundry. Endless possibilities with the unfinished walkout basement. This home is ready for you to make it your own so bring your ideas! No need to wait, just pack your belongings and be home in time for the Holidays or start the New Year in a new home! Don't let this one get away.
